    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_09/sud_vo_adv_love_2505_05_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、私達は、人間に害をなす\nサキュバスを魔界に帰すのが目的だから\n害をなさない子は……どうしよう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "うーん、私達は、人間に害をなす\nサキュバスを魔界に帰すのが目的だから\n害をなさない子は……どうしよう？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.9666860863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
